                              <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS9430Tewodros">Tewodros</persName>
                              (on <locus target="#280r"/>). </desc>
                              <q xml:lang="am"/>
                            </item>
                            <item xml:id="a2">
                              <locus target="#4r"/>
                              <desc type="LandGrant">List of places bestowed by
                                <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS5617IyasuII">ʾIyāsu II</persName> to the
                                convent of <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LOC2246DabraB">Dabra Bǝrhān</placeName>.</desc>
                            <q xml:lang="gez"><seg part="I"/>
                            ኍልቈ፡ አህጉር፡ ዘወሀቡ፡ ወጐለቱ፡ ለደብረ፡ ብርሃን፡ በስመ፡ ሥሉስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ አብ፡
                            ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ አሐዱ፡ አምላክ። ንጉሠ፡ ነገሥት፡
                            <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS5617IyasuII">አድያም፡ ሰገድ፡</persName>
                            ዘበጸጋ፡ ተሰምዩ፡ ኢያሱ።
                          </q>
                            </item>
                            <item xml:id="a3">
                              <locus target="#4r"/>
                              <desc type="Record"/>
                              <q xml:lang="gez">
                                <seg part="I"/>
                                በዘመነ፡ ማርቆስ፡ <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS5617IyasuII">ሐፄ፡ ብርሃን፡ ሰገድ፡</persName>
                                በነገሡ፡ በ፮ ዓመት።
                              </q>
                            </item>
                            <item xml:id="a4">
                              <locus target="#5r"/>
                              <desc type="OwnershipNote">The note states that the manuscript belongs to the church of
                                  <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/INS0101MadhaneAlam">Madḫāne ʿĀlam</placeName>.</desc>
                              <q xml:lang="gez">ሐዊ፡ ዘ<placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/INS0101MadhaneAlam"> ቅዱስ፡ መድኃኔ፡ ዓለም።</placeName>
                        </q>
                            </item>
                          </list>
                          <list>
                            <item xml:id="e1">
                              <desc>At the foot of some pages occur names prefixed with a relative pronoun, probably
                              those of scribes. For example,
                              ዘ<persName role="scribe" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS13103Dawit">ዳዊት፡</persName>
                              (on <locus target="#27r #37r"/>),
                              ዘ<persName role="scribe" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS13104SardaKesos">ሠርፀ፡ ክሶስ፡</persName>
                              (on <locus target="#47r #56v #57r"/>),
                              ዘ<persName role="scribe" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS13105YamanaKrestos">የማነ፡ ክርስቶስ፡</persName>
                              (on <locus target="#157v #158r"/>),
                                ዘ<persName role="scribe" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS13106MalkeaKesos">መልክዓ፡ ክሶስ፡</persName>
                                (on <locus target="#169r"/>),
                            ዘ<persName role="scribe" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS13108Agnateyos">አግናጥዮስ፡</persName>
                            (on <locus target="#240r"/>),
                            ዘ<persName role="scribe" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS13109AmdaM">ʾAmda Mikāʾel</persName>አምደ፡ ሚካኤል፡</desc>
                            </item>
                          </list>

